    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Zhang Z., Vaupel J., 2009, “The Age Separating Early Deaths from Late Deaths”, Demographic Research, 20, 721—730.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
